Lesson 4, last Exercise:

Deduplication!

• Sort
• Compare with previous

import csv
animals = []
for state, animal in csv.reader(open('Data/state-animals.csv')):
    animals.append(animal)

animals.sort()

previous = ''
for animal in animals:
    if animal != previous:
        previous = animal
        print(animal)



